(11051, 'Réflexions sur le mouvement « gabberskins »Une première approche sociologique', 'titre_article', 6, '&lt;r2r:ml lang=&quot;en&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;abstract&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Since about three years, some young peoples, the &ldquo;Gabberskins&rdquo;, make the front pages of local newpapers by their racist violence in the small town of Chauny, a small city of the North of France. The situation deteriorated so much that national newspapers were interested in these events. Indeed, &ldquo;Gabberskins&rdquo; shock by their clothing racist signs, by their insults or by racist tags. So, we will analyze in this article the reasons for this growth, its origins, the ideology underlying recovery and that attempts by extreme right parties.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/r2r:ml&gt;;'),
